---
title: Souvlaki-Inspired Pork Bowls with Yogurt Sauce
description: Briny feta and creamy yogurt sauce add lots of Greek-inspired flavour to this pork bowl. Peppers, onions and marinated pork on fluffy, buttery and brothy rice will remind you of your favourite takeout souvlaki
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-de-porc-facon-souvlaki-8e96a97d.jpg
